        Reproduces "Manufacturing Form.xlsx" / Sheet "1 LSHW- FXI-F1" exactly:
        every cut-list line's formula (in terms of L, H, window Qty and a few
        yes/no options) was read straight from that sheet's cell formulas.
        This is a starting point users can freely edit/extend from the
        Window Templates screen; it will not be overwritten by module updates.
    -->

